title: Republicans turn down volume on Trump's tax cuts
text:
Republicans turn down volume on Trump's tax cuts 4:34pm IST - 01:36
Republican incumbents in the tightest congressional races in the November elections are talking less and less about the tax cuts, a Reuters analysis shows. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
